definition: to come/to arrive/to come round/ever since/next
to speak/to explain/to negotiate/to emphasise/to be particular about/as far as sth is concerned/speech/lecture

sentences.english: But for property buyers are concerned, it is common snipe mussels competing and profit.
sentences.chinese: 但对于购房者来讲，却是鹬蚌相争，渔翁得利。

sentences.english: Nani's passage to the World Cup with Portugal was plain sailing by comparison with Evra's exertions.
sentences.chinese: 纳尼进入世界杯比起埃弗拉来讲就顺理成章的多。

sentences.english: From this perspective, design patterns have much to offer.
sentences.chinese: 从这一点来讲，设计模式可以提供很多好处。

sentences.english: Usually, the lives of black women go largely unexamined.
sentences.chinese: 通常来讲，黑人女性的生活并不受人关注。

sentences.english: In a sense, arithmatic is a language.
sentences.chinese: 某种意义上来讲，算术是一种语言。

sentences.english: You spin the story another way,and I follow the personality.
sentences.chinese: 你换一种方法来讲，我又认同了人格理论。

sentences.english: This single building on Daizongfang terms of architectural art is relatively high.
sentences.chinese: 就岱宗坊这一单体建筑来讲，建筑艺术也是比较高的。

sentences.english: On one level, this is not surprising.
sentences.chinese: 从某种层面上来讲这毫不足奇。

sentences.english: Therefore, in its origin, Standby was a substitution of bank guaranties.
sentences.chinese: 因此，从起源上来讲，备用证的产生是出于替代。

sentences.english: Personally I hope you’ll accept this clause.
sentences.chinese: 从我个人来讲，我希望你们接受这一条款。

sentences.english: Personally, I agree with the suggested conventions.
sentences.chinese: 就个人来讲，我同意所提议的约定。

sentences.english: How much does tuition cost in general?
sentences.chinese: 总体上来讲，学费是多少？

sentences.english: From the point of view of parachuting, the wing is actually a branch of parachuting.
sentences.chinese: 从跳伞角度来讲，其实翼装是跳伞运动的一个分支。

sentences.english: Will tell from the taste, the biggest characteristic is TaiCan drizzle.
sentences.chinese: 从口味来讲，酸辣是泰餐最大的特点。

sentences.english: So, to finish up today, we won't get through all of it.
sentences.chinese: 今天课快要结束了，我们不会展开来讲它。

sentences.english: Although I keep saying the first star is the brightest.
sentences.chinese: 虽然，我从来讲，第一颗星最亮。

definition: regarding/as far as sth is concerned/with regards to
to come and see/to see a topic from a certain point of view
in fact/in reality/as a matter of fact/in practice
to speak/to explain/to negotiate/to emphasise/to be particular about/as far as sth is concerned/speech/lecture
after all/all in all/when all is said and done/in the final analysis
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
